<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a7Sep1924"><font color="red">7 September 1924</font> <i>BLHW</i> (insert): In hoc Signo Vinces &ldquo;Oh, Church of the Irish! as ye are children of Christ, so be ye children of Rome.&rdquo; &mdash; St. Patrick. Breastplate of St. Patrick I, &hellip;&hellip;, rise up today The Shield of God protecting me from the hand of every man who plots against me, near or far, alone or with others. Christ be with me. Christ be before me.  Christ be after me. Christ be above me. Christ be at my right hand. Christ be at my left hand. Christ be in the fort. Christ be in the chariot. Christ be in the ship. Christ be in the heart of every man who thinks of me. Christ be in every eye that sees me. Christ be in every ear that hears me. Permissu Ordinarii Dioce. Dublinen. (All rights reserved.) </div>
